Progress update: Cover all UniProt prefix permutations: add URL-style xref branch

Audited all permutations of xrefs/is_about, intermediate resolution,
and UniProt prefix formats. Added a new UNION branch for URL-style
UniProt xrefs (https://www.uniprot.org/uniprotkb/*/entry) found on
